      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that's a good start. specifically, i want to make sure i can shut down any counter-arguments in the essay. like, if someone tries to bring up the idea of meritocracy or says that wealth is just a result of individual hard work, how can i frame those views as being fundamentally wrong or even harmful to the cause of racial justice?",
